[resource]
script = ExtResource("1_tf8mg")
reagent_id = "CO"
title = "Carbon monoxide"
body = "[b]Basic facts[/b]
[table=2]
[cell]Formula:[/cell][cell]CO[/cell]
[cell]Molar mass:[/cell][cell]28 g/mol[/cell]
[cell]State at room temperature:[/cell][cell]Gas[/cell]
[cell]Color:[/cell][cell]Colorless[/cell]
[cell]Smell:[/cell][cell]Odorless[/cell]
[/table]
[b]Formation reaction[/b]
C + CO₂ → 2CO
[b]Important properties[/b]
• Highly toxic gas.
• Produced during incomplete combustion of carbon fuels.
• Flammable and burns in oxygen.
[b]Where carbon monoxide is found[/b]
• Produced by car engines.
• Formed when coal, gas, or wood burns without enough oxygen.
• Can accumulate in poorly ventilated spaces.
[b]Uses[/b]
• Used in industrial chemical processes.
• Important in the production of fuels and chemicals.
[b]Safety[/b]
Very dangerous because it is colorless and odorless.
Prevents blood from carrying oxygen, which can cause serious poisoning or death."
